date: '2009-03-03 11:30:43 -0800'
comment: You can't in general translate Unicode characters 1:1 to ASCII.  For instance,
  ร doesn't translate to "s", it translates to "ss".  Furthermore, you might want
  to handle multiple transliterations, to allow "รถ" to match either "oe" or "o".

